					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13970735#post-4863143</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13970735/scp-5607#post-4863143</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 05 Jan 2021 20:18:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>not_a_seagull</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3009022</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Is this goofy as hell? Yes. No self-respecting shadow government organization would name a device PISS. Did I thoroughly enjoy it nonetheless? Yes. The log at the end drags a little in the middle, but the story overall keeps a consistent voltage and once again explores a lateral take on weaponizing anomalies.</p> <p>In addition, this opens up a Project Crossover scenario where the Foundation manhunts Dale Gribble for hoarding copious quantities of SCP-5607-1.</p> <p>+1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
